lyrics:
(Verse 1)
Grand Admiral Thrawn he's on the prowl
Coming for Luke Skywalker gonna make him howl
With his strategic mind he'll pound and strike
Turning Jedi dreams into a sleepless night

“Thrawn's got a hunger a craving so deep
To open up Luke's cockpit and feast while he sleeps
back  to mouth, he'll taste the force within
Fulfilling his mission to strategically win”

(Chorus)
Thrawn's on the attack, Jedi beware
He'll go straight for the back hole, no room for error
In the heat of battle, he'll unleash his power
Conquering Luke's cockpit.
